Paper: hep-th/0002142

Date: 2000-02-17

Title: Logarithmic Conformal Field Theories Near a Boundary

Authors: S. Moghimi-Araghi and S. Rouhani

Comments: 9 pages, no figures, Latex, references added, typos corrected

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 53 (2000) 49-57

We consider logarithmic conformal field theories near a boundary and derivethe general form of one and two point functions. We obtain results forarbitrary and two dimensions. Application to two dimensionalmagnetohydrodynamics is discussed.